<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 18:08:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伊朗核武器、10 月 7 日和内塔尼亚胡：鲁莽的遗产</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/irans-nukes-october-7-and-netanyahu-a-reckless-legacy/0000018c-d4a9-d4e1-ad8f-fcb9c7000000</link><description>正如以色列总理拒绝为导致哈马斯屠杀的鲁莽行为承担责任一样，他也拒绝为放弃他自己视为毕生使命的问题承担责任。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:21:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/irans-nukes-october-7-and-netanyahu-a-reckless-legacy/0000018c-d4a9-d4e1-ad8f-fcb9c7000000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院命令政府部长放弃解雇以色列邮政主席</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/supreme-court-orders-government-ministers-to-abandon-israel-post-chairman-firing/0000018c-d4e9-daf6-a5df-d7fd6be90000</link><description>两名利库德集团议员坚持在战争期间解雇以色列邮政主席米沙尔·瓦克宁，尽管有证据表明邮政服务在他的指挥下正在改善。瓦克宁和《华盛顿邮报》认为，推翻他的企图是政治性的</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:18:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/supreme-court-orders-government-ministers-to-abandon-israel-post-chairman-firing/0000018c-d4e9-daf6-a5df-d7fd6be90000</guid></item><item><title>在国际法院指控以色列犯有种族灭绝：请愿书、先例和惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/charging-israel-with-genocide-at-the-icj-petition-precedents-and-punishment/0000018c-d449-ddba-abad-d6e91a480000</link><description>南非为何向海牙国际法院提交针对以色列在加沙行为的请愿书？为什么以色列有兴趣配合诉讼程序？可能的结果是什么？</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:59:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/charging-israel-with-genocide-at-the-icj-petition-precedents-and-punishment/0000018c-d449-ddba-abad-d6e91a480000</guid></item><item><title>格罗斯曼、齐泽克等公众人物签署反对“巴勒斯坦人和以色列人非人化”的信</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/public-figures-sign-letter-against-the-dehumanization-of-palestinians-and-israelis/0000018c-d47c-ddba-abad-d6fdf7d20000</link><description>“亲人类阵营联盟”反对“10月7日犯下的暴行”，也反对将所有加沙人与哈马斯等同起来，“哈马斯利用哈马斯为不分青红皂白的杀戮和拒绝人道主义援助合理化”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/public-figures-sign-letter-against-the-dehumanization-of-palestinians-and-israelis/0000018c-d47c-ddba-abad-d6fdf7d20000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质重返 10 月 7 日改变他们生活的现场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-return-to-the-scenes-that-changed-their-lives-on-october-7/0000018c-d4aa-d4e1-ad8f-fcbb05d10000</link><description>在三个月前被哈马斯摧毁的贝埃里基布兹这次不寻常的旅行中，游客也是主要受害者：“这是我自 10 月 7 日以来第一次来到贝埃里。经历了这一切之后我很难再来这里”我们已经经历过&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 13:54:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-return-to-the-scenes-that-changed-their-lives-on-october-7/0000018c-d4aa-d4e1-ad8f-fcbb05d10000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院的加沙种族灭绝案有一个不知情的盟友：以色列政客</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/gaza-genocide-case-at-the-icj-has-an-unwitting-ally-israeli-politicians/0000018c-d479-d4e1-ad8f-fcf93ae90000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡本可以要求他的部长们闭嘴，不要再说有关加沙的蠢话。相反，他忽视甚至鼓励他们。他欢迎南非向国际法院提出的轻率请求，因为这证明了他的“世界反对我们，这不是我的错”的说法是正确的</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 13:52:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/gaza-genocide-case-at-the-icj-has-an-unwitting-ally-israeli-politicians/0000018c-d479-d4e1-ad8f-fcf93ae90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列卫生部表示，自 10 月 7 日袭击事件以来，自杀率并未出现飙升</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/no-spike-in-suicide-rates-since-oct-7-attack-israeli-health-ministry-says/0000018c-d404-daf6-a5df-d77c0d980000</link><description>根据法医研究所收集的部分数据，卫生部的声明显示，有迹象表明，过去三个月的自杀人数甚至低于平时。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 12:23:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/no-spike-in-suicide-rates-since-oct-7-attack-israeli-health-ministry-says/0000018c-d404-daf6-a5df-d77c0d980000</guid></item><item><title>待在室内：希伯伦居民面临着前所未有的限制，无法离开家园或社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hebron-residents-face-restrictions-like-never-before-unable-to-even-leave-their-homes/0000018c-d3db-daf6-a5df-d7ff8aab0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，以色列实施的限制导致生活在约旦河西岸城市以色列控制地区的希伯伦居民无法前往工作场所，甚至无法购买食物。军队声称希伯伦没有宵禁，但现实却并非如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 12:20:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hebron-residents-face-restrictions-like-never-before-unable-to-even-leave-their-homes/0000018c-d3db-daf6-a5df-d7ff8aab0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列杂志刊登漫画，描绘前最高法院院长在加沙踩士兵背</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-magazine-runs-cartoon-depicting-ex-top-court-president-stepping-on-soldiers-back/0000018c-d3fc-d4e1-ad8f-fffda54e0000</link><description>该杂志主要由宗教犹太复国主义读者阅读，收到了法院管理法律顾问的一封措辞强硬的信，认为这可能相当于“煽动暴力”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 11:58:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-magazine-runs-cartoon-depicting-ex-top-court-president-stepping-on-soldiers-back/0000018c-d3fc-d4e1-ad8f-fffda54e0000</guid></item><item><title>“儿童的处境更加艰​​难”：严重的饥饿正在加沙蔓延。来自人类灾难的四种声音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/severe-hunger-is-spreading-in-gaza-four-voices-from-a-human-catastrophe/0000018c-d3da-d4e1-ad8f-fffbf0800000</link><description>加沙不可能的现实：营养不良而无法母乳喂养的母亲在爆炸的威胁下寻找食物，援助组织在压力下崩溃</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 10:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/severe-hunger-is-spreading-in-gaza-four-voices-from-a-human-catastrophe/0000018c-d3da-d4e1-ad8f-fffbf0800000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡因偏执而制定的法律即将被扔进历史的垃圾箱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-paranoia-induced-law-is-on-its-way-to-historys-dumpster/0000018c-d39f-daf6-a5df-d7ff6e7f0000</link><description>总检察长将保留宣布总理内塔尼亚胡不适合任职的能力，但高等法院法官没有澄清她在什么情况下可以这样做。 10 月 7 日之后以色列内塔尼亚胡政府的公众舆论表明她似乎不太可能会这样做</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 10:35:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-paranoia-induced-law-is-on-its-way-to-historys-dumpster/0000018c-d39f-daf6-a5df-d7ff6e7f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人应该为了自己的利益而停止战争，即使不是为了加沙的利益。</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israelis-should-want-to-stop-the-war-for-their-own-sake-if-not-for-gazas/0000018c-d37e-ddba-abad-d3ff951d0000</link><description>精神卫生服务不堪重负，教育系统半运转不灵，经济衰退，企业倒闭，枪支事故令人不安，犯罪率上升。即使大多数以色列人不会为了加沙人而反对战争，他们也最好开始考虑战争给自己的生活带来的巨大损失</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 09:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israelis-should-want-to-stop-the-war-for-their-own-sake-if-not-for-gazas/0000018c-d37e-ddba-abad-d3ff951d0000</guid></item><item><title>高等法院的新裁决：内塔尼亚胡家族所有恐惧的总和</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/high-courts-new-ruling-the-sum-of-all-fears-for-netanyahu-family/0000018c-d109-ddba-abad-d3a9fabc0000</link><description>在阻止废除合理性标准两天后，以色列最高法院还废除了旨在剥夺总检察长宣布总理不适合任职的法律选择的法律。至少在战争期间，内塔尼亚胡计划的反对以色列民主的政变已经因法官席上的自由派多数而停止</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 04:01:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/high-courts-new-ruling-the-sum-of-all-fears-for-netanyahu-family/0000018c-d109-ddba-abad-d3a9fabc0000</guid></item><item><title>在美国压力下，以色列考虑开放埃雷兹过境点以提供加沙人道主义援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/under-u-s-pressure-israel-weighs-opening-erez-crossing-for-gaza-humanitarian-aid/0000018c-d0f5-daf6-a5df-d7fd7e190000</link><description>这将直接向加沙北部的居民提供援助，该地区获得的援助远不如南部那么多。以色列国防军控制了加沙北部的大部分地区，并且可以确保哈马斯无法劫持援助卡车并自行保留物资，这与南部地区不同。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 04:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/under-u-s-pressure-israel-weighs-opening-erez-crossing-for-gaza-humanitarian-aid/0000018c-d0f5-daf6-a5df-d7fd7e190000</guid></item><item><title>真主党希望避免全面战争，贝鲁特暗杀事件束缚了纳斯鲁拉的手脚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/beirut-assassination-ties-nasrallahs-hands-as-hezbollah-hopes-to-avoid-all-out-war/0000018c-d11e-ddba-abad-d3bff3c10000</link><description>在达希耶有针对性地杀害哈马斯的阿鲁里和六名恐怖分子，向真主党和伊朗发出信号，表明以色列确信它已为黎巴嫩战争做好了充分准备。这并不是一个无足轻重的风险，这也是受到加沙战斗的影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 04:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/beirut-assassination-ties-nasrallahs-hands-as-hezbollah-hopes-to-avoid-all-out-war/0000018c-d11e-ddba-abad-d3bff3c10000</guid></item><item><title>国防部长告诉美国高级特使，以色列“更愿意通过外交解决方案”而不是与真主党发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-live/white-house-u-s-to-leave-significant-mideast-presence/0000018c-d284-d4e1-ad8f-feb548930000</link><description>以色列国防军司令：黎巴嫩前线已做好充分准备 ■ 以色列 MK 称，由于美国压力，自 2024 年初以来，以色列军队的行动有所不同 ■ 来自黎巴嫩领土的反坦克导弹击中北部城市梅图拉的房屋 ■ 至少 300 人在图尔卡姆营地被捕约旦河西岸居民称 ■ 国际法院定于下周就加沙种族灭绝案件举行公开听证会 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵被杀；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 22,313 人死亡、57,296 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 03:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-live/white-house-u-s-to-leave-significant-mideast-presence/0000018c-d284-d4e1-ad8f-feb548930000</guid></item><item><title>中东紧张局势接近白热化，美国加大力度打击红海胡塞武装</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-steadily-boosts-efforts-against-houthis-in-red-sea-as-middle-east-tensions-near-boil/0000018c-d162-ddba-abad-d3e3dcf10000</link><description>拜登政府因未能对胡塞武装的侵略做出足够的反应而受到一些前美国官员和国会议员的批评</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 22:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-steadily-boosts-efforts-against-houthis-in-red-sea-as-middle-east-tensions-near-boil/0000018c-d162-ddba-abad-d3e3dcf10000</guid></item><item><title>尽管哈马斯领导人被暗杀，以色列高级官员对人质协议谈判仍持“乐观”态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/top-israeli-official-optimistic-about-hostage-deal-despite-hamas-leaders-killing/0000018c-d0db-daf6-a5df-d7ffe0b80000</link><description>这位资深消息人士还表示，以色列部长最近敦促巴勒斯坦人从加沙地带“自愿移民”的言论是“妄想”，以色列正在为国际法院的听证会做准备，并考虑向伊朗、南非和真主党请愿。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 20:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/top-israeli-official-optimistic-about-hostage-deal-despite-hamas-leaders-killing/0000018c-d0db-daf6-a5df-d7ffe0b80000</guid></item><item><title>被以色列拘留的加沙人数量一个月内猛增 150%；目击者：士兵在军事设施中虐待被拘留者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/number-of-gazans-detained-in-israel-jumps-150-witness-soldiers-abuse-detainees/0000018c-ca0b-d6c4-ab8d-ebbf60380000</link><description>661 名加沙人被拘留在以色列监狱中，此外还有数量不明的人被关押在斯德泰曼基地的军事设施中。一位熟悉那里情况的消息人士称，士兵正在殴打被拘留者，并将他们铐在栅栏上</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 19:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/number-of-gazans-detained-in-israel-jumps-150-witness-soldiers-abuse-detainees/0000018c-ca0b-d6c4-ab8d-ebbf60380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子因性侵犯被捕，据称使用了他通过宽松的枪支法规获得的枪支</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/man-arrested-for-sexual-assault-allegedly-used-gun-he-obtained-through-lax-regulations/0000018c-d09a-daf6-a5df-d7fe044b0000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，本·格维尔部制定的宽松规定已向约 30 万份枪支申请和 5 万份许可证发放。 《国土报》报道称，其中 14,000 个许可证是非法颁发的</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 19:17:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-03/ty-article/.premium/man-arrested-for-sexual-assault-allegedly-used-gun-he-obtained-through-lax-regulations/0000018c-d09a-daf6-a5df-d7fe044b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>